      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just drama, my head really hurts and i feel super congested. if it's just hormones, then why are doctors so strict about it? if i just took one or two tablets to get through the night, would it really be that big of a deal for the baby? i'm just so tired of feeling like this.",
